test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert -3721 == -61
 +  where -3721 = <built-in function prod>([-61, -1, -61])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (0 == 3)
 +  where 0 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x749e6847af00>([-61])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x749e6847af00> = [[1, -61], [1, -61, 1], [-61, 1], [-61, 1, -61], [1, -61], [1, -61, 1], ...].count
